items.name: Time Slider - LoRA
items.description:
• weight: -8.0 to 8.0 (or more)

  • positive: into the future

  • negative: into the past

High weights go forward, negative weights go back, like a time machine. One issue is that it cannot go back much farther than the 50s or 60s, unfortunately, there are just not a lot of pictures before then that SD was trained on, for whatever reason :). Pictures can also go greyscale or get orange. Add "monochrome" to the negative prompt to help combat that. Going forward, everything gets silver. Silver clothes, silver walls, etc.

If you like my work, I'm not asking for coffee, but a good review is always appreciated.

items.name: Mineru [Tears Of The Kingdom]
items.description:
The rep images include a prompt sweep across a fixed seed; this isnt a bias thing, its to demonstrate the token changes specifically.

Pretty happy with this one. The only thing i am going to improve is to get her mouth/snout to be more zonai and less generalized. there is a strong chance my choice of artists in the prompt may be preventing this feature from developing and others may bring it out.

The main image should have all the data that ive trained in. everything that isnt related to the setting or image style, i.e. specific character descriptors, are necessary for getting the likeness. i didnt tokenize her skirt or blouse so that will have to be left up to rng.

the main token elements is the collar/necklace, mask, and floating scarf. p.s. use negatives, the mask likes to stick around if you dont.

mineruwear is the name of the concept where she is mostly clothed in her canonical apperance.

it can sometimes struggle to produce the third eye.

items.name: Sindel Mortal Kombat Embedding
items.description:
Sindel debuts in MK3 as the queen of Edenia alongside her daughter, Princess Kitana, but her kingdom loses ten consecutive Mortal Kombat tournaments and is invaded by Shao Kahn, resulting in a forceful merging of the two realms. After her husband King Jerrod is killed and their then-infant daughter Kitana is adopted by Kahn, she commits suicide rather than become his consort. Kahn resurrects her with the assistance of the sorcerer Shang Tsung in Earthrealm, allowing Kahn to invade Earthrealm while regaining his queen in the process. Sindel is successfully revived but in a brainwashed state with no knowledge of her past. After the Earthrealm defenders defeat Kahn, Kitana convinces Sindel her of her true past, turning Sindel against the emperor.

Likeness seems to improve with the additions in the prompt: "gray hair" and "purple and black outfit".

I find her more similar to MK 11 when using this TI with realistic models, but the results with other kind of models is interesting too.

items.name: 【再世】next life-龙方
items.description:
这是群星再世第四十七期，以后会不定期出去世的群星Lora，以纪念他们。

从《上海滩赌神》中的黄金贵，到《赌神》中的高义，再到《雷洛传》中的流氓头子，龙方通过他独具特色的表演，将诸多反派形象深深地烙在观众的心中。龙方很早入行，但是反响平平，就退圈远赴美国开了一家餐厅，自己当餐厅经理，后来被向华强重金邀请回香港帮他打理旗下的海鲜餐厅天天渔港，担任经理，而王晶开拍《至尊无上》时找不到反派演员，在朋友介绍下龙方接拍了《至尊无上》那个日本人角色。

而后王晶再邀龙方拍《赌神》，电影的成功让人记住了「奸人」龙方。从此一发不可收拾，「坏人」片约接踵而来。龙方也正式辞职，做起了全职演员。2000年后龙方开始在大陆经商，做回了生意。香港电影是少了个奸人，多了份遗憾。

他还被称为“反刘德华专用演员”，因为只要他和刘德华演戏，就一定是各种折磨刘德华，连他妻子看了他的戏都问他是不是真的黑社会成员。用龙方自己的话来总结就是：我是奸人世家，谁能奸过我？我疯起来，连我自己都害怕。


图4的香港影视剧中最常出现的恶人，已经全部去世。

2008年，龙方因癌症去世，享年54岁。

items.name: Billions of Characters Extension - clothing, summer, revealing, sexy, mature
items.description:
IMPORTANT: This is an extension for the base wildcards of Billions of Characters.

With YAML-files you just get 1 nice wildcard-file Instead of 100 files. They are easy readable (best with Notepadd++) and they are easy to maintain.

Don't forget to leave a ❤️ to get a notification for future updates. ⭐ reviews are appreciated, too. Let me see what you created with this tool. ;)

This set focuses only on clothing. The focus is summer clothing, swimwear, a bit nsfw clothing and sexy clothing. It includes lighting settings and (sexy) poses, too, to get the right mood.

note: Yaml files will throw isseus when using: "a1111-sd-webui-tagcomplete"extension. That's related to the extension, not the wildcards.

Usage

Unleash the full power: 

Activate: Dynamic Prompts->Advanced Options->Unlink seed from prompt

Usage is pretty much the same as for "regular" wildcards.

You need the SD Dynamic Prompt Extension. Put the files directly into the wildcard folder:

~\stable-diffusion-webui\extensions\sd-dynamic-prompts\wildcards

They show up as a menu on the left in the Wildcards tab.

The YAML is structured and indented (that's how they work). Just with a little difference. You have to add the category layers in the wildcard.

Examples:

__clothings-nsfw/female-attire__
__clothings-nsfw/male-attire__
__nsfw/lighting__

A cool thing you can do, too, is using a wildcard "*" in the wildcards. So you could use clothings from the normal BoChars wildcards, too. You'll get clothings from both sets (or all subsets, if present):


__clothings*/female-attire__ # for clothings from both/all sets/subsets

You'll find a full list of options below.

You are welcome

Leave a star review, if you like it. so other can find those awesome cards more easily.

I plan to do some more subsets for different themes (like my magical characters). They'll be extensions to this base wildcards.

SDXL is coming, and wildcards are limitless.

If you want to support me, feel free to buy me a coffee. ;)

Keep in mind, that those are only wildcards. Your model might not have learned all of the items.

Have fun experimenting with it.

items.name: 浦和ハナコ(水着) | 碧蓝档案 blue archive
items.description:
右上角打开“everything”模式可以查看更多封面图片

 我不知道花子的泳装图为什么被吞掉！这个lora确实是泳装版本，如果你没有看到我发的图片，大概率是平台审核不通过，但是我并没有露出任何敏感的地方

I'm not sure why the picture of Huazi in a swimsuit was removed! This Lora model is indeed a swimsuit version. If you didn't see the picture I posted, it's likely that it didn't pass the platform's review process. However, I didn't expose any sensitive areas.

这个模型可以在保留角色特征的情况下实现换装，或者不覆盖任何衣物。

This model can achieve outfit changing while preserving the character's features, or without covering any existing clothing.

这是碧蓝档案的花子的泳装形态，因为目前训练的数据集有限，还不能做到很好的还原。

因为我在训练是打的是全标，因此你如果想调动该角色，有以下标签是你必须添加的。

必需的positive prompt ：

<lora:swhuazi_v1:0.8>,huazi, girl, breasts, pink hair, green eyes, solo,long hair, braid, ahoge

创作出泳装形态需要的positive prompt ：

<lora:swhuazi_v1:0.8>，huazi, 1girl, shirt, solo, large breasts, cleavage, white shirt, smile, bow, hair bow, blush, water, wet clothes, wet, see-through long sleeves,wet shirt, collared shirt, very long hair side braid

建议权重：0.8

右边这个是角色浦和ハナコ的 sdxl版本

我并不建议你下载这个模型，这个模型仅仅是一个不成熟的lora！

这个模型的起因是我想测试如果用同样的训练集，相似的参数，sd1.5和sdxl模型训练出来lora区别会多大。

从效果上来看，说不上很好，也说不上很差。

我准备了15张数据集，repeat为20，batch为8，ep为2。

我在训练时准备了263张正则化图片，这些图片搜集自pixiv。

我的训练脚本是https://github.com/bmaltais/kohya_ss。

我训练的设备是3090双卡训练。

训练一次大概是20分钟左右。

从测试上来看，这个lora的最佳权重是0.8。

这个lora会出现时而二次元，时而三次元的情况。

该lora在1000以上分辨率，效果会大大变好。

我对sdxl训练并不熟练，我正在找出导致这个情况发生的原因。

This is the swimsuit form of Huazi, but due to the limited training dataset, it cannot be accurately reproduced at the moment.

Since I used full tags during training, there are certain tags that you must add if you want to generate this character.

These are the required positive prompts:

<lora:swhuazi_v1:0.8>， huazi, girl, breasts, pink hair, green eyes, solo, long hair, braid, ahoge.

To create the swimsuit form, you will need the following positive prompts: <lora:swhuazi_v1:0.8>，huazi, 1girl, shirt, solo, large breasts, cleavage, white shirt, smile, bow, hair bow, blush, water, wet clothes, wet, see-through long sleeves, wet shirt, collared shirt, very long hair side braid.

It is recommended that you use a weight of 0.8 for these prompts.

This is the sdxl version of the character Hanako Puruha.

I do not recommend downloading this model, as it is an immature LORa model.

The reason for this model is that I wanted to test the difference between using the same training set and similar parameters to train LORa models in SD1.5 and SDXL.

In terms of performance, it's neither good nor bad.

I prepared 15 datasets with a repeat of 20, batch size of 8, and 2 epochs.

During training, I prepared 263 regularized images collected from Pixiv.

My training script is available at https://github.com/bmaltais/kohya_ss. ↗

I trained the model using a 3090 dual-card device, and each training session took about 20 minutes.

From testing, the best weight for this LORa model is 0.8.

This LORa model can sometimes produce two-dimensional or three-dimensional results.

The performance of this LORa model greatly improves at resolutions above 1000.

I am not proficient in SDXL training and am currently trying to identify the cause of this situation.
